ance risk  6 explain Security risk  7 explain Privacy risk  8 explain Science vs execution risk  9 explain Operational fragility  6️⃣ SOLUTION ARCHITECTURE & SYSTEM DESIGN  1 explain Workflow Core components.  2 explain Data logic Human vs automation   Feedback loops Defensibility Scalability model. 3 explain Cost curve Unit economics Bottlenecks Failure modes.  7️⃣ PROBLEM–SOLUTION FIT : explain User disappointment risk Workarounds Willingness to pay Budget clarity Validation signals Retention likelihood Habit formation. Expansion potential Fit Score (0–10).   8️ TARGET USER & DISTRIBUTION REALITY: 1explain ICP User vs buyer Decision maker.  2 explain Decision cycle . 3explain  Behavioural inertia.  4explain Status quo bias.  5 explain Switching friction \n. 6 explain Distribution channels.  7 explain CAC risk.  8 explain Trust barrier.  9 explain Network growth potential.  10explain Founder-led sales need Segment realism ."
